Package: sparkle
Type: Package
Title: Client-Side Reactive Framework for R with React
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A client-side reactive framework that enables R developers to create
    interactive web applications using R syntax. Sparkle runs entirely in the browser
    via webR and uses React for rendering. Inspired by Shiny but without server requirements.
